member.example:
This sample shows how to call EightAsync.

Uri endpoint = new Uri("<https://my-service.azure.com>");
Qux client = new ServiceClient(endpoint, ClientType.Default).GetQuxClient();

Response response = await client.EightAsync();

Console.WriteLine(response.Status);

This sample shows how to call EightAsync with all request content.

Uri endpoint = new Uri("<https://my-service.azure.com>");
Qux client = new ServiceClient(endpoint, ClientType.Default).GetQuxClient();

Response response = await client.EightAsync();

Console.WriteLine(response.Status);

